{"tid":724950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人掹衫尾入閘　網民怒斥有錢購物無錢買車飛","createTime":"2018-07-01T10:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T12:56:15.000Z","uid":2547,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"556c7c8f5b2656d342440a01a2451413e428cf73","tid":724950,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JaW1oQxAUtw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJaW1oQxAUtw&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2Fjklm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=93e28eaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JaW1oQxAUtw</a><br />\n<br />\n網民Jackson今日（1日）在「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」群組上載影片，聲稱在港鐵尖沙咀站，目擊兩名疑為內地自由行的男女，「跟人衫尾出閘」。他跟隨對方至尖東站時，發現對方用同樣的手法，趁其他乘客拍卡入閘時，緊貼其後「同步入閘」。目擊者稱當時立即向港鐵職員投訴，「可惜捉唔到人」，又怒斥片中人「真係好憎啲大陸人有錢購物，無錢買地鐵飛！」又質疑「可能係近來流行嘅手法！」 <br />\n<br />\n不少網民反駁，「用呢啲方式唔係今時今日嘅事，好多站都係有，但唔明點解冇職員看管。」同時批評目擊者為何只顧拍片，未有主動上前截停對方。目擊者則回應指「可惜我真係好趕時間，如果唔係就實捉住佢哋。」也有人表示曾在佐敦站目擊過類似事件，「阿伯行得慢，拍卡後個賤人衝出...個阿伯反而出唔到，要搵港鐵職員幫手！」直指同類情況司空見慣，認為港鐵職員應多加巡查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f344ee7a0277d8b0ce8acc678dcf696e0d8d4d","tid":724950,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10fbd68c5079c5e8a8dd971cae22afdd6afed210","tid":724950,"uid":53577,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"黑警話大陸人唔垃得，含緊大陸撚嘅淋病落咗order."},{"pid":"9632b7e59099bf2358d67ad7602827d9a7cc6ed6","tid":724950,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"細個睇唔記得大雄定小新都係咁入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來現實都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1159a018c2806eb4bdd96d3c3ecba2f12d65086","tid":724950,"uid":34334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3cbcfab604df4ea0a4903969d34b45cf6ab07ee","tid":724950,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b37d2674f7107b2fed3228a23a0a0e3ce2d79f","tid":724950,"uid":76471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"暫時諗唔到返咗咩罪<br />\n<br />\n有罪就可以行使市民拘捕權"},{"pid":"f500c431b6c4bacf50db41281c0602a70c5560e7","tid":724950,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"其實拍完片有證據做乜唔上前截停佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da40c55a14582e986e4b3b59fa5a5f9440c2f8c2","tid":724950,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"我見過有人喺機場快線香港站 <br />\n<br />\n身貼身出閘 慳返 幾十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5628bf1f81b7ee8c4069f45c4b56ed7394561af5","tid":724950,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"咁短時間都出到？俾我實食佢身位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e078488360110eda1343b3987268b79c239cce","tid":724950,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"東鐵果隻機就唔驚喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a967e560ce6385b1ab4e0d91302fc102bfa52962","tid":724950,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5628bf1f81b7ee8c4069f45c4b56ed7394561af5","tid":724950,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T12: